457.3.0.0_CustomerSupport_FAQ.question.1.en: Can I book a taxi through hotlink?

457.3.0.0_CustomerSupport_FAQ.answer.1.en: No. Taxi bookings are only available in the Zig app.

457.3.0.0_CustomerSupport_FAQ.question.2.en: Are infants subject to the taxi seating capacity policy?

457.3.0.0_CustomerSupport_FAQ.answer.2.en: Infants between 0 and 12 months can be carried, therefore are not considered as passengers and are not subject to the taxi seating capacity policy.

457.3.0.0_CustomerSupport_FAQ.answer.2.h.en: Find out more about the seating capacity of our taxis here

457.3.0.0_CustomerSupport_FAQ.answer.3.en: No. According to the Singapore Police Force, taxis are exempt from the child-seat requirement.
